{"tid":1256400,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我有一個愚問：民意","createTime":"2019-06-25T04:06:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T06:33:42.000Z","uid":197235,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6999629127869f7818555e2417dad2ccaa65d4a","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:06:36.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得民意係抗爭一開始用作招募人手，當你人手足夠就唔應該太着重，太著重好容易影響你既決定，當然要挽回，不過要係成功之後，唔應該行動一次，就道一次歉，令市民覺得我地係真心悔改，覺得自己做錯咗。你話人地玩民意戰，但係我覺得你地兩方只係爭取緊中立又唔會企出嚟既人，要選票更加唔應該比人見到自己既弱勢。我寧願你地向市民打氣，都唔好道歉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔啱就請指出，想交流唔係分化<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘義士丶烈士，626我地再賭多次一定要到</span></span>"},{"pid":"f7e1063b83471eb9703d34ac13a0093937c8b154","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"愚見，交流不分化"},{"pid":"27ca6b90fcd91066e4b17e3b8ae29c473724812d","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:08:18.000Z","msg":"香港人唔好放棄"},{"pid":"742f7b4d949068d4e383ac92b2e1c69510ac8611","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:08:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得會有同我同樣諗法既人"},{"pid":"14724dd2d42cf3c129f37bc2f690b6c1bbcc72ee","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1458f01f54aab2959adfb5918be96b84c80d3895","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7508f5ca7073c0d49dab9b115a735c9ac1b62c20","tid":1256400,"uid":197235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T04:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"924307a1b6d74c67569149dec5cda29200f1f86a","tid":1256400,"uid":19723